  "Description": {
    "English": "The coiled remains of a <span class=\"name name-special\">Hungering Tendril</span>'s digestive tract. Though its meaty walls still convulse, there is surely no way for a fresh tendril to regrow from these meager scraps...<br><br>Such specialist offal is rarely traded on the Galactic Exchange and is thus <span class=\"name name-stellar\">highly valuable</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一根<span class=\"name name-special\">饥饿的触手</span>的消化道残骸。虽然上面的肉壁依旧在不停抽搐，但是这些残渣绝不可能复原成真正的触手......<br><br>银河交易所中极少能见到这种特殊脏器，因此拥有着<span class=\"name name-stellar\">十分宝贵</span>的价值。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一根<span class=\"name name-special\">飢渴觸手</span>消化束的蜷曲殘骸。儘管它多肉的內壁依舊在蠕動，但這堆貧弱的遺骸不可能再長出一根新觸手的......<br><br>如此特殊的內臟遺骸在銀河交易所內相當罕見，因此<span class=\"name name-stellar\">極度珍貴</span>。"
  },
